      "content": "Each <bpt id=\"p13\">***</bpt><bpt id=\"p14\"/>trainable layer<ept id=\"p14\">***</ept><ept id=\"p13\"/><ph id=\"ph7\"/> (a hidden or an output layer) has one or more <bpt id=\"p15\">***</bpt><bpt id=\"p16\"/>connection bundles<ept id=\"p16\">***</ept><ept id=\"p15\"/>. A connection bundle consists of a source layer and a specification of the connections from that source layer. All the connections in a given bundle share the same <bpt id=\"p17\">***</bpt><bpt id=\"p18\"/>source layer<ept id=\"p18\">***</ept><ept id=\"p17\"/><ph id=\"ph8\"/> and the same <bpt id=\"p19\">***</bpt><bpt id=\"p20\"/>destination layer<ept id=\"p20\">***</ept><ept id=\"p19\"/>. In Net#, a connection bundle is considered as belonging to the bundle's destination layer.",
      "nodes": [
        {
