        2724
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p23\">**</bpt>Convolutional bundles<ept id=\"p23\">**</ept>. The user can define small neighborhoods of nodes in the source layer. Each node in the destination layer is connected to one neighborhood of nodes in the source layer.",
      "nodes": [
        {
          "content": "<bpt id=\"p23\">**</bpt>Convolutional bundles<ept id=\"p23\">**</ept>.",
          "pos": [
