      "content": "The layers <bpt id=\"p196\">_</bpt>Gather<ept id=\"p196\">_</ept><ph id=\"ph89\"/> and <bpt id=\"p197\">_</bpt>Result<ept id=\"p197\">_</ept><ph id=\"ph90\"/> are destination layers in multiple connection bundles."
