      "content": "The output layer, <bpt id=\"p198\">_</bpt>Result<ept id=\"p198\">_</ept>, is a destination layer in two connection bundles; one with the second level hidden (Gather) as a destination layer, and the other with the input layer (MetaData) as a destination layer."
