      "content": "The arity of the convolution is three (the length of the tuples <bpt id=\"p214\">**</bpt>InputShape<ept id=\"p214\">**</ept>, <bpt id=\"p215\">**</bpt>KernelShape<ept id=\"p215\">**</ept>, <bpt id=\"p216\">**</bpt>Stride<ept id=\"p216\">**</ept>, and <bpt id=\"p217\">**</bpt>Sharing<ept id=\"p217\">**</ept>)."
