      "content": "The number of weights per kernel is <bpt id=\"p218\">_</bpt>1 + <bpt id=\"p219\">**</bpt>KernelShape<ept id=\"p219\">**</ept>\\[0] * <bpt id=\"p220\">**</bpt>KernelShape<ept id=\"p220\">**</ept>\\[1] * <bpt id=\"p221\">**</bpt>KernelShape<ept id=\"p221\">**</ept>\\[2] = 1 + 1 * 5 * 5 = 26. Or 26 * 50 = 1300<ept id=\"p218\">_</ept>."
